articles.title: Hannity: Biden's 'half-baked' Afghanistan withdrawal plan will get Americans killed - Fox News
articles.description: Fox News host Sean Hannity pulled no punches tearing into President Biden's “half-baked” Afghan withdrawal Wednesday, blaming the administration for the “thousands” of deaths that are expected to occur as a result of the botched U.S. evacuation.
